) flowers basal, borne in pairs; male inflorescence with longer peduncle (
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD2E16EFB26FAC2684FE9A1" box="[1263,1351,1988,2015]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" unit="cm" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2‚Äì3 cm</quantity>
) flowers apical on short cymes branching 3‚Äì4 times; protogynous. 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD2E16EFCD5FAEE6E62E67C" bold="true" box="[796,874,2024,2050]" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">Bracts</emphasis>
deciduous, light green, basal pair lanceolate, 9‚Äì11 √ó 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD2E16EFF69F50A6C08E659" box="[160,256,2060,2087]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" unit="mm" value="2.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="2.0">2‚Äì3 mm</quantity>
, margin entire. 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD2E16EFE78F50A6F76E658" bold="true" box="[433,638,2060,2086]" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">Staminate flower</emphasis>
: pedicel 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD2E16EFD2EF50A6E4DE659" box="[743,837,2060,2087]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="5.0">5‚Äì7 mm</quantity>
long; tepals 2, pink, orbicular, 4‚Äì5 √ó 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD2E16EFB39F50A6858E659" box="[1264,1360,2060,2087]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="259" unit="mm" value="4.5" valueMax="5.0" valueMin="4.0">4‚Äì5 mm</quantity>
, margin entire, apex rounded; androecium actinomorphic; stamens 15‚Äì20, golden yellow; filaments 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFBB7FD9869F9EEC7" box="[1150,1265,158,185]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="1.25" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="0.5">0.5‚Äì2 mm</quantity>
, slightly fused at base; anthers very widely obovate, apex truncate to round, 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD3E16FFCD6FDC56E48EEA2" box="[799,832,195,220]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="260">ca.</emphasis>
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFC8EFDC46EA9EEA3" box="[839,929,194,221]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="1.5">1.5 mm</quantity>
. 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD3E16FFC65FDC4696FEEA2" bold="true" box="[940,1127,194,220]" pageId="3" pageNumber="260">Pistillate flower</emphasis>
: pedicel 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFB07FDC4682AEEA3" box="[1230,1314,194,221]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="cm" value="5.0" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="4.0">4‚Äì6 cm</quantity>
long; tepals 5, pink, obovate to elliptic, 11‚Äì15 √ó 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFDE4FDE06F93EF7F" box="[557,667,230,257]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="11.0" metricValueMin="4.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="7.5" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="4.0">4‚Äì11 mm</quantity>
, margin entire, apex acute; ovary light green to pink, elliptic, 10‚Äì14 √ó 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFF68FC0C6C05EF5B" box="[161,269,266,293]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.1" metricValueMin="0.9" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="10.0" valueMax="11.0" valueMin="9.0">9‚Äì11 mm</quantity>
(wings excluded), 3-locular, placentation axile; 3-winged surrounding and extending beyond the ovary, wings pink, equal; styles 3, golden yellow, 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD3E16FFDAAFC296F8CEF36" box="[611,644,303,328]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="260">ca.</emphasis>
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFD43FC286FC1EF37" box="[650,713,302,329]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="3.0">3 mm</quantity>
long, apically 2-cleft; stigmas in a spiral band. 
<emphasis id="B913EAC7FFD3E16FFB1BFC28683AEF36" bold="true" box="[1234,1330,302,328]" pageId="3" pageNumber="260">Capsule</emphasis>
trigonouselliptic, 30‚Äì38 √ó 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFE8CFC546CBCEF13" box="[325,436,338,365]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.8" metricValueMax="3.6" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="cm" value="28.0" valueMax="36.0" valueMin="20.0">20‚Äì36 cm</quantity>
including wings; pedicel 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFD1BFC546E2DEF13" box="[722,805,338,365]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="cm" value="6.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="5.0">5‚Äì7 cm</quantity>
long; wings 3, equal, truncate to rounded distally, cuneate proximally, 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFEC6FC706C80EFEF" box="[271,392,374,401]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.4" metricValueMax="3.8" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="34.0" valueMax="38.0" valueMin="30.0">30‚Äì38 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity id="4C9F9B30FFD3E16FFE07FC706F4FEFEF" box="[462,583,374,401]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.4" metricValueMax="1.8" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="3" pageNumber="260" unit="mm" value="14.0" valueMax="18.0" valueMin="10.0">10‚Äì18 mm</quantity>
wide.
</paragraph>
